{"type": "article", "id": 59880, "title": "用做蛋糕的技巧做花瓶，效果如何？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2019-01-01T22:56:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 15258, "name": "Missana"}, {"id": 55582, "name": "点造"}, {"id": 55583, "name": "Chris Hardy"}, {"id": 55584, "name": "Tim Teven"}, {"id": 978, "name": "Raf Simons"}, {"id": 55585, "name": "Erika Emeren"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 50, "image": "img/article/article_show/201901012024096TdbKJiZ98XLs1lm.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #5264a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #5264a8} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #5264a8; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #5264a8} span.s7 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s8 {font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} span.s9 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; text-shadow: 1.0px 1.0px 0.0px #ffffff} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。 </p><h3>Ornament Now: Cake Vases by Erika Emeren</h3><p>埃因霍温设计学院的毕业生 Erika Emeren 将传统的蛋糕制作技术变成了一种制作独特陶瓷花瓶的方法。这一系列花瓶名为 Ornament Now: Cake Vases，通过使用做蛋糕的技巧将粘土附着在纸张旋转形成的圆筒上，就像制作糕点和蛋糕装饰的方法一样，也是瑞典传统甜点 Spettekaka 的制作方法。</p><p>之后，Erika Emeren 再将每个花瓶烧制并上釉，以形成光滑且色彩鲜艳的饰面。这个过程意味着每只花瓶都具有独特的形状。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203256O84YKrjt5syJEnVD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901012025126pPEFX52Ybf430BJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101202514WBoPb1thw7ikFjOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101202516bDfGd9CcrHg548NA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101202559gFmeVlP3iB1J0yN7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/12/31/erika-emeren-spit-cake-vases-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>“椅moji”小动物椅子 by 点造</h3><p>新年伊始，点造推出新年限量款“椅moji”小动物椅子，既是家具，也是孩子最好的朋友。</p><p>每次去动物园，孩子的眼睛都闪着光，对大自然的爱，对动物的亲近感，与生俱来。“拟人化”的设计，在家具中加入情感连结，每天使用的日常之物，也可以是孩子最好的朋友。正坐是椅子，反坐是玩具，正坐、侧坐、反坐，小动物椅子 360 度无死角，怎么使用，由孩子做主。</p><p>6 种样式：小狗，小鹿，小象，小兔子，小狮子，小团圆，总有一款萌到你。椅子高度有 24cm 和 30cm 两种选择，3 岁以下孩子适合 24cm 高，3 岁以上适合 30cm 高。售价 499 元，<a href=\"https://yishucollection.heidianer.com/products/dotmake-newyear?from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=0\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101202923oVbcE87mfFhXaL5s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101202924FLNB3RCwG7JD8rtT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101202924Uc981ky32RKsMEFB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101202925P5Om7HLfQsTUgzEh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101202925HojGs4mz7ft2P9ZR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101202926Iw6pGT7XDJ9kenA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101202926BWAgtdVfE9PyUpha.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901012029275HENvwDjc6uQkmS9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Silver Half Crushed Can Keychain by Raf Simons</h3><p>知名设计师 Raf Simons 带来了一组造型独特的钥匙扣。这组易拉罐造型的钥匙扣，兼具 DIY 文化与雕塑艺术，视觉上十分简洁，仅在其底部以及挂钩细节处刻有品牌名，且亮银色能够适合多种场合使用。</p><p>而看似随意压扁而成的易拉罐，其实是经过精雕细琢才如此的写实。钥匙扣选用的材料为铝，在意大利制造完成，售价 365 美元，<a href=\"https://www.ssense.com/en-us/men/product/raf-simons/silver-half-crushed-can-keychain/3521899?ranMID=41610&amp;ranEAID=9ieob0c66Uo&amp;ranSiteID=9ieob0c66Uo-8wmosN.rVIJ3OCUu_UxhLw&amp;utm_source=ls_APAC_9ieob0c66Uo&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=generic&amp;utm_term=1&amp;siteID=9ieob0c66Uo-8wmosN.rVIJ3OCUu_UxhLw\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203008tFLZmfSVhvkGOjIy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203009Snk8mVfoGUCWd6vi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203009OE9tYvPFl74W2zMj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Recycling Reject Project by Tim Teven</h3><p>埃因霍温设计学院的毕业生 Tim Teven 开发了一种使用从纸纤维中分离出来的废物制作家具和积木的方法。</p><p>Tim Teven 的回收废品项目，灵感源自他在荷兰访学期间，他注意到了纸张回收设施，并发现回收过程中产生了大量工业废料，比如塑料和木材，与纸分离并作为废物收集。Teven 决定专注于寻找一种方法，来重复使用这种材料，创建可用于制作家具和其他物体的模块，并将其与矿物基颜料和粘合剂混合，再压缩成一系列模具。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203038B97cDbkYAz4q3ZPN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203041m6D8UWQCLZAcfMYJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203042tGDUFb64JPcm5A2a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203116F7oZJHp6UvDickrV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://timteven.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tim Teven Studio</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Alce Collection by Chris Hardy for&nbsp;Missana</h3><p>扶手椅和沙发是装饰客厅两个必不可少的家具。西班牙家具品牌 Missana 推出最新系列家具 Alce，注入澳洲风情，带来清新的极简主义体验。操刀 Alce 系列的是澳洲设计师 Chris Hardy。</p><p>这一清新极简的系列，以简洁的线条和圆润的形状为基础，并融入了不同的独立元素。这符合 Chris Hardy 关于个性、简约和设计可定制的理念，以创造出引人注目且极具吸引力的产品。Alce 最特别的部分，是其柔软、圆润的靠背和座垫，与围绕沙发的独特纤薄铁结构的强烈对比，意在视觉效果上创造趣味性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203209jNJlM3DeT58LSQmd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203211BQ3FN7IrcaGXsqiU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201901012032125A8tpCj2F3OJY4aP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203212Fpn25hLmWgQ96I8M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203213PCxqXUg02lazc6Ju.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203213P9weHWG7XskYrzjV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203214UWeED4qBsLJd3lC7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190101203215SsC4rz0m9Lq5hMUR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.missana.es/en/15-modelos-en/395-alce-en\" rel=\"nofollow\">Missana</a></figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}